nodes.text: Robin Atkin Downes (born September 6, 1976) is an English Actor and Voice actor who plays a role in The Clone Wars.

He has had roles in various TV shows, movies, and video games, such as Babylon 5, Team Fortress 2, Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen, Uncharted, Prince of Persia: Warrior Within, No More Heroes, Gears of War, Gears of War 2, Metal Gear Solid: Peace Walker and Valkyria Chronicles.
